：2026-04-09\n\n## 1. 背景与目标\n\n### 背景\nSocial World 是一款面向年轻人群的
陌生人社交应用，核心定位是通过高效的滑动匹配和即时通讯帮助用户建立新的社交关系。
\n\n### 目标\n在 V1 MVP 阶段，实现最小可用的陌生人社交闭环：\n- 用户可以注册登录
并完善个人资料\n- 系统为用户推荐附近的异性/同性用户卡片\n- 用户可以通过左滑/右滑
表达喜好\n- 双向喜欢的用户可以开始一对一聊天\n\n## 2. 用户故事与验收标准\n\n### 
US-1：注册与登录\n\n**作为** 新用户，**我希望** 通过手机号快速注册登录，**以便**
开始使用 App。\n\n#### 验收标准\n```gherkin\nFeature: User Authentication\n  Sce
nario: New user registers with phone number\n    Given the user opens the app fo
r the first time\n    When the user enters a valid phone number and SMS code\n  
 Then an account should be created\n    And the user should receive an access to
ken\n    And the user should be redirected to profile setup\n\n  Scenario: Exist
ing user logs in\n    Given the user already has an account\n    When the user e
nters the phone number and correct SMS code\n    Then the user should receive ne
w tokens\n    And the user should land on the home screen if profile is complete
\n```\n\n#### 技术要求\n- 使用 JWT Token（Access 15min + Refresh 7天）\n- 短信验
证码 MVP 阶段可先用固定码（如 `123456`）或接入阿里云短信\n- 手机号作为唯一用户标
识\n\n---\n\n### US-2：完善个人资料\n\n**作为** 用户，**我希望** 上传照片并填写
个人资料，**以便** 被别人发现和匹配。\n\n#### 验收标准\n```gherkin\nFeature: Use
r Profile\n  Scenario: User completes minimum profile\n    Given the user has ju
st registered\n    When the user uploads an avatar, enters nickname, selects gen
der and birth date\n    Then the profile should be marked as complete\n    And t
he user should enter the home screen\n\n  Scenario: Incomplete profile blocks ma
tching\n    Given the user has not completed minimum profile\n    When the user 
tries to swipe cards\n    Then the system should prompt the user to complete pro
file first\n```\n\n#### 资料字段\n- 必填：头像、昵称、性别、出生日期、当前位置\n
- 选填：个人签名、相册（最多6张）、兴趣标签（最多8个）、匹配偏好（性别、年龄范围
）\n\n#### 技术要求\n- 头像和照片上传至对象存储（阿里云 OSS / AWS S3）\n- 照片上
传后经过内容安全审核（MVP 阶段可先人工延后审核，预留接口）\n- 用户需满 18 周岁（
根据 birth_date 计算）\n\n---\n\n### US-3：推荐卡片与滑动匹配\n\n**作为** 用户，
**我希望** 看到附近有趣的异性/同性用户卡片，**以便** 通过滑动选择喜欢或跳过。\n\
n#### 验收标准\n```gherkin\nFeature: Card Swipe Matching\n  Scenario: User sees 
recommendation cards\n    Given the user is on the home screen with complete pro
file\n    When the app loads\n    Then the user should see a stack of profile ca
rds sorted by distance and activity\n\n  Scenario: User likes a profile\n    Giv
en the user sees a card\n    When the user swipes right or taps the like button\
n    Then a like action should be recorded\n    And if the other user already li
ked this user, a match should be created\n\n  Scenario: Mutual like creates a ma
tch\n    Given Alice liked Bob and Bob liked Alice\n    When the system detects 
the mutual like\n    Then a match record should be created\n    And a conversati
on should be auto-created\n    And both users should receive a match notificatio
n\n```\n\n#### 推荐规则（MVP）\n1. **过滤条件**：\n   - 根据用户设置的偏好性别筛
选\n   - 根据当前位置，默认半径 50km（可切换「同城」「全国」）\n   - 排除已经 Li
ke / Pass / Block 过的用户\n   - 排除已经匹配成功的用户\n   - 排除资料不完整的用
户\n2. **排序规则**：\n   - 距离越近越优先（权重 50%）\n   - 近期活跃用户优先（
权重 30%）\n   - 新用户有额外曝光加成（权重 20%）\n3. **卡片展示**：\n   - 首图
（头像或相册第一张）占卡片主要区域\n   - 叠加显示：昵称、年龄、距离、个性签名\n\
n#### 技术要求\n- 推荐池缓存于 Redis（TTL 5 分钟），减少数据库查询压力\n- 地理位
置使用 MySQL `decimal` 存储经纬度，通过 Haversine 公式计算距离（MVP 简化方案）\n
- 滑动操作幂等处理（防止重复提交）\n\n---\n\n### US-4：即时通讯（IM）\n\n**作为*
