e on GitHub\n\n---\n\nTitle: widgetbook_golden_test 0.3.0 | Flutter package\nDat
e: 2025-04-02\nURL: https://pub.dev/packages/widgetbook_golden_test/versions/0.3
.0\nSummary: This library automates the creation of golden tests for Flutter wid
gets using Widgetbook use cases generated in the directories file. These files a
re\xa0...Read more\n\nThis library automates the creation of golden tests for Fl
utter widgets using Widgetbook use cases generated in the directories file. Thes
e files are\xa0...Read moreAutomatically generate Flutter golden tests from Widg
etbook use cases generated by the widgetbook\\_generator.\n\nThis library automa
tes the creation of golden tests for Flutter widgets using Widgetbook use cases 
